#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/pin.rst:4
msgid "Pin the KV cache"
msgstr "固定 KV Cache"

#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/pin.rst:6
msgid "The ``pin`` interface is defined as the following:"
msgstr "``pin`` 接口定义如下："

#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/pin.rst:12
msgid ""
"The function pins (persists) the KV cache chunks specified by ``tokens`` "
"in the given ``location`` of the ``instance_id``. The controller returns "
"an ``event_id`` and the number of tokens scheduled for pinning."
msgstr "该函数将指定的 ``tokens`` 在给定的 ``instance_id`` 的 ``location`` 中固定（持久化）KV Cache 块。控制器返回一个 ``event_id`` 和计划固定的令牌数量。"

